    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i'll take a look at the rotors. but i'm also just spooked by the sound itself. it's such a weird, piercing noise that it almost sounds almost... intentional? like it's purposefully trying to be annoying. does that make sense or am i just overthinking a mechanical sound?",
